author: Brie Stimson
title: Gretchen Whitmer clarifies stay-at-home order after Meghan McCain slam
description: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer clarified Sunday that the state’s updated stay-at-home order doesn’t ban buying child car seats after Meghan McCain slammed the governor and retweeted a claim that it did.
